window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Author Mark Lawrence has won over audiences everywhere with <i>Prince of Thorns</i>, his exciting debut novel. </p> <p>Nine-year-old Prince Jorg is forced to watch as his mother and brother are slaughtered. Fleeing the palace, Jorg joins a bloodthirsty band of thugs. But he’s determined to take back what’s rightfully his, so he returns to the castle a few years later - unaware of the dark and powerful magic that awaits.</p>"; 
